The paper discusses the challenges of privacy, trust, and resilience in decentralized IoT solutions for transactive microgrids. This suggests that the paper may belong to the categories of cryptography (cs.CR), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), systems and control (cs.SY), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
